Seniors received insurance assistance through SHIP

  98,868 Seniors received services through our Area Agencies

  2,130,078 meals were delivered to home bound seniors

 

How can we help you?

We provide several state and local programs through our Area Agencies on Aging.  Read more about our programs below or visit one of our ADRCs.

Aging and Disability Resource Centers (ADRC)

Disaster

Preparedness

Assistance

Long Term Care

Prescription Drug Assistance

How can you help others?

If you want to help serve the seniors and disabled in your community, then our SMP and SHIP programs can give you the opportunity.

 

Learn More

We have 13 Area Agencies on Aging across Alabama to serve the

needs of our Seniors, each with an Aging and Disability Resource Center (ADRC).

Visit yours today
